<Answer 2>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--[if lt IE 7]>      <html class="no-js lt-ie9 lt-ie8 lt-ie7"> <![endif]-->
<!--[if IE 7]>         <html class="no-js lt-ie9 lt-ie8"> <![endif]-->
<!--[if IE 8]>         <html class="no-js lt-ie9"> <![endif]-->
<!--[if gt IE 8]>      <html class="no-js"> <!--<![endif]-->
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <title>Registration Form</title>
    <meta name="description" content="" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <style>
      .required {
        color: red;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!--[if lt IE 7]>
      <p class="browsehappy">
        You are using an <strong>outdated</strong> browser. Please
        <a href="#">upgrade your browser</a> to improve your experience.
      </p>
    <![endif]-->
    <table border="5px" , align="center">
      <th>Fields</th>
      <th>Data</th>

      <tr>
        <td>First Name:<span class="required"> * </span></td>
        <td><input type="text" placeholder="Enter first name" required /></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Last Name:</td>
        <td><input type="text" placeholder="Enter last name" /></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Mobile:<span class="required"> * </span></td>
        <td><input type="text" placeholder="Enter last name" required /></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Email:<span class="required"> * </span></td>
        <td><input type="email" placeholder="Enter Email here" required /></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Date of Birth:</td>
        <td><input type="date" /></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Password:<span class="required"> * </span></td>
        <td><input type="password" /></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Password:</td>
        <td><input type="password" /></td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Country:</td>
        <td>
          <select>
            <option value="India">India</option>
            <option value="USA">USA</option>
            <option value="Japan">Japan</option>
            <option value="China">China</option>
          </select>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>
          Qualification (select 1 or more than one):<span class="required">
            *
          </span>
        </td>
        <td>
          <ul style="list-style-type: none">
            <li>
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                name="qualification"
                value="graduate"
              />Graduate
            </li>
            <li>
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                name="qualification"
                value="post-graduate"
              />Post Graduate
            </li>
            <li>
              <input type="checkbox" name="qualification" value="phd" />PhD
            </li>
          </ul>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>Gender:<span class="required"> * </span></td>
        <td>
          <input type="radio" name="gender" value="male" required /> Male
          <input type="radio" name="gender" value="Female" required /> Female
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>
          <button type="submit" value="submit">Register</button>
        </td>
        <td>
          <button type="reset" value="reset">Cancel</button>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <br />
    <br />

    <script src="" async defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
